data.description: Welcome to this 1900 classic Cleveland colonial home conveniently located near highways and shopping. The 1,866 SF are home to 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The spacious living room combines with the formal dining room. The dining room includes a custom built in, a decorative original fireplace, and an inrush of natural light. Newer hardwood floors continue into the kitchen. The kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, ample storage, and sliding doors to the wood deck. The first floor bedroom with full bathroom can be used as an additional entertainment space, office, or your very own first floor master suite. Placed on the second floor you will find the other 3 bedrooms and full bath. The attic and unfinished basement are perfect for extra storage. There is unlimited potential here, don’t miss out! Schedule your private showing today!
